ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T16:16:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">名古屋呀 燕窩月餅<br />\n低卡 好味 健康 又fit啲</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱啱想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真問架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc65b089a010aeff31cb0300a189ab510f03cdc5","tid":6554,"uid":4549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T16:17:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想買吓嘢食吓嘢個人覺得大須商店街幾好。<br />\n唔太迫，幾好行，而且本身名古屋唔多遊客去，耐唔耐先撞到吓香港人，唔似大阪東京咁樣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThx mark定先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105c668875c7a3d255293cd2b2167e154dc72384","tid":6554,"uid":8122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:04:46.000Z","msg":"鐵道館<br />\n岐阜城<br />\n琵琶湖"},{"pid":"b3bbf8e8e4f825c191940e57fc740566f0af50f2","tid":6554,"uid":3131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:05:12.000Z","msg":"佢海邊個水族館我覺得幾靚 可能因為我之前未去過水施館 <br />\n想食野嘅去下名古屋站嘅地下街 好多出名嘅食肆果到都有 <br />\n試下佢個 三食曼魚飯 係ok 嘅 一場黎到 點都試下 <br />\n佢名古屋城後面一個公園 係名古屋城站落就到 <br />\n個公園好悠閑有時間可以去睇下 <br />\n名古屋成個城市都唔多人 又唔迫 <br />\n散心唔錯"},{"pid":"544ac91b1d80f4db0ea503b68d16275c295a5b2b","tid":6554,"uid":20048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:06:38.000Z","msg":"個市立科學館都好正，可以玩一日"},{"pid":"d2b5fc56a1780d5e2526f037d0738df14ff45354","tid":6554,"uid":4549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4954b5ababc84a5cfed9a3591e2fdedec28130","tid":6554,"uid":20048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T05:13:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>豐田博物館</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢有兩個<br />\n一個係郊區，好似叫auto city, 擺左幾百部古董車，車迷必去<br />\n一個係市區，好似叫技術館，講豐田起家既織布機，聽落好似悶，但正過古董車<br />\n因為有tour guide, 同埋有得落手玩，趣味大好多"}]}